<section id="donate">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Donate</p>
    <h2>Give once, monthly, or as part of your estate</h2>
    <div class="split" style="margin-top:32px">
      <div class="prose">
        <h3>Monetary gifts</h3>
        <p>Give online any time, or mail a check to:<br><strong>The Caring Place, Inc.</strong><br>Advocacy Center<br>607 Bullseye Lake Road<br>Valparaiso, IN 46383</p>
        <h3 style="margin-top:28px">Recurring &amp; planned gifts</h3>
        <p>Memorial gifts, estate gifts through our Beacon Circle, and Qualified Charitable Distributions from an IRA are all ways to make a lasting impact. Call 219-464-0840 (memorial gifts) or 219-464-0840 x103 (QCDs) to arrange.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:32px 30px">
          <h3>Ready to give?</h3>
          <p style="margin-top:10px">Every gift — big or small — funds shelter, advocacy, and community education.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-clay" style="margin-top:20px" href="https://fundraise.givesmart.com/form/lrINrA?vid=12g272" rel="noopener">Donate Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="volunteer" class="helpband">
  <div class="wrap split">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Volunteer</p>
      <h2>We need you. Your skills and time are valuable.</h2>
      <p>Volunteer opportunities change as new needs arise — from shelter support to events and administrative help. Tell us a bit about yourself and we'll follow up about current openings.</p>
      <p class="phone-cta" style="font-size:19px">Questions? Call 219-464-0840<br><span style="font-size:15.5px;font-weight:400">Administrative office, 8am–4pm</span></p>
    </div>
    <form class="gethelp" method="POST" action="/thank-you/" name="volunteer-inquiry" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="volunteer-inquiry">
      <p style="position:absolute;left:-9999px"><label>Leave this field blank<input name="bot-field"></label></p>
      <h3 style="font-size:22px">Volunteer inquiry</h3>
      <div><label for="v-name">Name<input id="v-name" name="name" type="text" required></label></div>
      <div><label for="v-email">Email<input id="v-email" name="email" type="email" required></label></div>
      <div><label for="v-phone">Phone<input id="v-phone" name="phone" type="tel"></label></div>
      <div><label for="v-interest">What interests you?<textarea id="v-interest" name="interest"></textarea></label></div>
      <button class="btn btn-teal" type="submit">Send inquiry</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="in-kind">
  <div class="wrap">
