    <h2>Give goods through our partners</h2>
    <p style="margin-top:16px;max-width:62ch">When our shelter doesn't currently need specific items, we refer in-kind donors to our partner resale shops in the Valparaiso area — your donation still supports our work through their proceeds.</p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card"><h3>New Creation Resale Shop</h3></div>
